Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: transparent; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pln&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;　　　10,20{sed-commands} &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 对10到20行操作,包括第10,20行&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: transparent; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pln&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;　　　10，+20{sed-commands} &amp;nbsp; 对10到30(10+20)行操作,包括第10,30行&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: transparent; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pln&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;　　　1~2{sed-commands} &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 对1,3,5,7,……行操作&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: transparent; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pln&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;　　　10，${sed-commands} &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 对10到最后一行($代表最后一行)操作,包括第10行&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: transparent; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pln&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;/oldboy/{sed-commands} &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 对匹配oldboy的行操作&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: transparent; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pln&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;/oldboy/,/Alex/{sed-commands} &amp;nbsp;对匹配oldboy的行到匹配Alex的行操作&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; background-color: transparent; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pln&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box