mp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.3.2 文本替换&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 10px 20px; font-size: 17.5px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-family: &amp;#39;Crete Round&amp;#39;, serif; line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;s：单独使用→将每一行中&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;第一处&lt;/strong&gt;匹配的字符串进行替换 ==&amp;gt;sed命令&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;g：每一行进行全部替换 ==&amp;gt;sed命令s的替换标志之一，非sed命令&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;-i：修改文件内容 ==&amp;gt;sed软件的选项&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;sed软件替换模型&lt;/strong&gt;(方框▇被替换成三角▲)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;sed -i &amp;#39;s/▇/▲/g&amp;#39; oldboy.log&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;sed -i &amp;#39;s#▇#▲#g&amp;#39; oldboy.log&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;观察特点&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol class=&quot; list-paddingleft-2&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;两边是引号，引号里面的两边分别为&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;s&lt;/code&gt;和&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;g&lt;/code&gt;，中间是三个一样的字符&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;/&lt;/code&gt;或&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;#&lt;/code&gt;作为定界符。&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;#&lt;/code&gt;能在替换内容包含&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;/&lt;/code&gt;有助于区别。定界符可以是任意符号如&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;:&lt;/code&gt;或&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;|&lt;/code&gt;等，但当替换内容包含定界符时，需转义即&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;:&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;|&lt;/code&gt;。经过长期实践，建议大家使用&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;#&lt;/code&gt;作为定界符。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;定界符&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;/&lt;/code&gt;或&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;#&lt;/code&gt;，第一个和第二个之间的就是被替换的内容，第二个和第三个之间的就是替换后的内容。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;s#▇#▲#g&lt;/code&gt;，▇能用正则表达式，但▲不能用，必须是具体的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;默认sed软件是对模式空间(内存中的数据)操作，而-i选项会更改磁盘上的文件内容。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;prettyprint linenums prettyprinted&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: brea